-Single responsibility use when some components can be used through a few pages and not to put all elements
to one class. Ex. divide a main page on main tabs component, search components ...
-Strategy pattern is good way to use when app provides multiple options to the user & based on the user
selection execute the business rule slightly differently. Ex. you can pay with card/paypal/money transfer...
-Template Pattern is useful when you need to test a lot of similar flows, then you need to create an abstract class
where define needed methods. Also with this class you can use Single Responsibility Pattern and Factory Pattern